  "instructions": [
    "Heat the vegetable oil in a medium pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the diced onion and sauté until translucent, about 3 minutes.",
    "Stir in the ginger paste and cook for another 30 seconds until fragrant.",
    "Add the diced tomato, bell pepper, and carrot, and cook for 4 minutes until they soften.",
    "Pour in the coconut milk and chicken broth, then bring to a gentle simmer.",
    "Add the jasmine rice, salt, and black pepper, stir to combine, then cover the pot.",
    "Reduce the heat to low, and simmer for 18 minutes until the rice is tender and the liquid is absorbed.",
    "Turn off the heat, let the stew sit covered for 5 minutes to steam further.",
    "Fluff the rice with a fork, then serve hot, garnished with fresh cilantro."
  ],
